org.apache.juddi.api.impl

Class API_141_JIRATest

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.juddi.api.impl.API_141_JIRATest

  • public class API_141_JIRATest
extends Object
    This test class provides test cases of items discovered or reported through the Juddi JIRA issue tracker The idea is that these tests apply to any UDDI registry and that the tests are either implied or derived requirements defined in the UDDI spec that were missed in other test cases for Juddi.
    Author:
    Alex O'Ree
